{"tid":1550794,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好想香港都可以有超級英雄","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T15:00:32.000Z","uid":205742,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f85d29a29a7f4dd9d991f6fe77db6506dbea417f","tid":1550794,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:41:23.000Z","msg":"有咩事都可以好似美國隊長咁樣企出嚟 用個盾幫我哋擋晒所有嘢 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好可惜喺香港企出來嘅人好多都已經俾人拉咗 我哋冇過人嘅能力 但係呢個世界只係得我哋係香港人 要保護呢達地方 捨我其誰 但當然如果無美國 呢場運動真係收咗皮 依家只可以等美國 而我哋都要做好我哋本分 聽日行去美領 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該都算係近嚟最和理非嘅一次活動啦 記得要smart casual<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e55257584cd58769995f7627b5eedc5c8ac99da","tid":1550794,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"272b0c9137e683f1a519172a85d644cd26cc6530","tid":1550794,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:42:08.000Z"